    10→ * - users.ts: Users, roles, sessions
    11→ * - operational-constraints.ts: Service demand, route utilization, unavailability, compatibility
    12→ * - track-capabilities.ts: Track capabilities, PM requirements, baseline assumptions
    13→ * - pm-management.ts: PM types, material requirements, PM schedule
    14→ * - mileage-tracking.ts: Meter events, mileage readings
    15→ * - component-tracking.ts: Train components, installations, component PM tracking
    16→ * - material-management.ts: Inventory positions, material reservations
    17→ * - manhour-planning.ts: Man-hour capacity, projections, adjustments
    18→ * - baseline-drift.ts: Plan baselines, baseline snapshots, drift analysis
    19→ * - scenarios.ts: Scenarios, deltas, comparisons
    20→ * - costing.ts: Labor rates, material costs, cost baselines
    21→ * - audit.ts: PM schedule history, audit log
    22→ *
    23→ * @see specs/003-database-schema.md for full schema specification
